cs.CR, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.DC 

This paper deals with security and attacks in cloud computing environments, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper specifically focuses on exploiting DRAM addressing for cross-CPU attacks, which involves hardware architecture (cs.AR) and system-level issues (cs.SY). The paper also involves reverse engineering and software automation, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
